divs: sighting detailswe go to a place and we can see objects flying in all different directions at high rates of speed, and at ultra high altitude, at any time of the year. these objects disappear, re-appear, and flash. my wife and daughter saw an oval shaped object flying over the navy base without making any noise, the day after 9\11. we wer at the beach sitting in loungers looking up some objects were space debri obviously but some were not we were excited to cee thede things and went back many times to see them
Summary: we see ufos any time we want we just go to a location where we see them and they are there all shapes and sizes
